---
// This is the ROOM Planetarium content component
---

  <!-- This is the ROOM Planetarium content component -->

  <section class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white tracking-wider text-center">ROOM Planetarium</h2>
    <h3 class="text-2xl mt-6 text-gray-300 tracking-wide text-center">Your Space Odyssey</h3>
  
    <!-- Project Description -->
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg leading-relaxed text-center">
      Introducing ROOM Planetarium, an immersive and educational app that invites users on a captivating journey through the cosmos. Crafted to blend cutting-edge technology with an engaging user experience, ROOM Planetarium offers a virtual odyssey into the universe's mysteries.
    </p>
  
    <!-- Key Features Section -->
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <!-- Feature 1: Augmented Reality Exploration -->
      <div class="bg-[#1b1b33] p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Augmented Reality Exploration</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Unveil the mysteries of our solar system with the power of Augmented Reality (AR). Immerse yourself in a stunning virtual universe where you can interactively explore celestial bodies and even manipulate their rotations.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Feature 2: Intuitive UI/UX Design -->
      <div class="bg-[#1b1b33] p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Intuitive UI/UX Design</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Seamless navigation and engaging interaction are at the heart of ROOM Planetarium's user interface, offering a smooth exploration of the cosmos.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Feature 3: Unique Interface Design -->
      <div class="bg-[#1b1b33] p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Unique Interface Design</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Thoughtfully crafted interactions and visuals provide a breathtaking experience, showcasing the beauty of the cosmos.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Feature 4: Captivating Animations -->
      <div class="bg-[#1b1b33] p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Captivating Animations</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          Mesmerizing animations elevate the user experience, making ROOM Planetarium a dynamic and immersive space journey.
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <!-- Feature 5: Stellar Sound Design -->
      <div class="bg-[#1b1b33] p-6 rounded-lg border border-gray-700 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all">
        <h4 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Stellar Sound Design</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
          The curated sound design complements the app's visual elements, offering an immersive auditory experience.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  
    <hr class="my-12 border-gray-600" />
  
    <!-- Visual Experience Section with Video -->
    <section class="relative mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white text-center">Feel the Sound and Visual Effects</h2>
      <iframe width="100%" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/u_h3aZ_qvfI" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen class="mt-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg"></iframe>
    </section>
  
    <!-- Buttons Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 mb-36 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
      
      <!-- GitHub Button -->
      <a href="https://github.com/jurilorenz/Room-Planetarium" class="bg-white text-[#090a1a] font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-200 transition-all">
        Check Project on GitHub
      </a>
  
      <!-- Back to Projects Button -->
      <a href="/projects" class="bg-[#1f1235] text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full border-2 border-[#6d87d1] shadow-lg hover:bg-[#6d87d1] transition-all">
        Go Back to Projects
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>